    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a strong engine and responsive transmission, having passed all recent safety inspections. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use on the driver's seat, and the exterior paint still looks great, though there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for daily driving without any immediate repairs needed.",
